        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
  <section id="services" class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-6 bg-linear-to-b from-white to-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Section Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
            Video Production Services
          </span>
          <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 px-4">
          Complete <span class="text-orange-400">Video Solutions</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
          From filming to final delivery, we handle every aspect of video production to create
          content that engages viewers and achieves your marketing objectives.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Services Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        {videoServices.map((service) => (
          <CardService
            icon={service.icon}
            title={service.title}
            description={service.description}
            learnMoreUrl={service.learnMoreUrl}
          />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tools & Technologies Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-4">
          Professional <span class="text-orange-400">Editing Tools</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We use industry-standard software and equipment to deliver broadcast-quality videos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6">
        {tools.map((tool) => (
          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-slate-50 to-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 text-center group">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              {tool.icon}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold text-cyan-900">{tool.name}</h3>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is Video Production Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 md:px-6 bg-linear-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
            <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">
              Understanding Video Production
            </span>
            <div class="h-px w-8 md:w-12 bg-linear-to-r from-transparent via-orange-400 to-transparent"></div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
            What is <span class="text-orange-400">Video Production?</span>
          </h2>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Video production is the comprehensive process of creating video content from initial concept through final delivery. It encompasses pre-production planning, filming or content creation, editing, post-production, and distribution optimization. Professional video production combines technical expertise with creative storytelling to create engaging content that captivates audiences and achieves marketing objectives.
            </p>

            <p>
              In today's digital landscape, video has become the most powerful medium for communication and marketing. Studies show that viewers retain 95% of a message when watched in video format, compared to just 10% when reading text. Video content generates 1200% more shares than text and images combined, making it an indispensable tool for businesses seeking to connect with their audience.
            </p>

            <p>
              Modern video production goes far beyond simple recording. It involves strategic planning, professional lighting, high-quality audio capture, creative cinematography, advanced editing techniques, color grading, motion graphics, sound design, and platform-specific optimization. Each element works together to create a polished final product that communicates your message effectively and maintains viewer engagement from start to finish.
            </p>

            <p>
              The rise of social media and online video platforms has transformed how businesses use video content. From short-form vertical videos for Instagram Reels and TikTok to long-form content for YouTube, from corporate presentations to product demonstrations, video production adapts to serve countless purposes across diverse platforms and audiences.
            </p>

            <p>
              Professional video production ensures your content stands out in an increasingly crowded digital space. Quality production values build credibility, enhance brand perception, increase engagement rates, and ultimately drive measurable business results including increased brand awareness, lead generation, and sales conversions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-900 to-cyan-800 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-8 text-white sticky top-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Video Marketing Impact</h3>

            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">86%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Of businesses use video marketing</div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">88%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Report positive ROI from video marketing</div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">2x</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">More likely to share video than other content</div>
              </div>

              <div class="border-l-4 border-orange-400 pl-4">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-400 mb-1">84%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-cyan-100">Were convinced to buy after watching a video</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-cyan-700">
              <p class="text-sm text-cyan-100 leading-relaxed">
                Video content is projected to account for 82% of all internet traffic, making professional video production essential for business growth.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <Whyus />

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-linear-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-4">
          Why Choose <span class="text-orange-400">Codebrand</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Our video production combines creativity, technical expertise, and marketing strategy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        {benefits.map((benefit) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="text-5xl mb-4">{benefit.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-3">{benefit.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{benefit.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-6 bg-linear-to-br from-cyan-900 via-cyan-800 to-cyan-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Ready to Create <span class="text-orange-400">Amazing Videos?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-cyan-100 mb-10 leading-relaxed px-4">
        Let's bring your vision to life with professional video production that engages audiences,
        tells your story, and drives business results. Get started on your video project today.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <Button text="Get Started Now" href="/contact" />
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/30 text-sm md:text-base">
          <span>View All Services</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <Faq />
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .delay-1000 {
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }
</style>
